premise_source_doc_sentence: But after a flurry of unexpected album content leaks , Madonna released the album for pre-order on the iTunes Store on December 20 , 2014 , with six songs being available immediately for download .
Following a commercial disappointment with her ninth studio album American Life in 2003 , Madonna released `` Hung Up '' , from her tenth studio album Confessions on a Dance Floor  (  2005  )  .
